Halika kung gayon.

264
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,080
Batiin natin si Ginang.

265
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,600
Dumiretso siya

266
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,080
kay Lola

267
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,039
yung sandaling lumabas ako?

268
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:13,279
Oo,

269
00:14:13,879 --> 00:14:14,320
Guro...

270
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:15,320
Meron pa.

271
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:18,039
Pumanaw na si Ginang

272
00:14:18,519 --> 00:14:19,159
ang iyong mga kaayusan sa pagpapakasal

273
00:14:19,159 --> 00:14:20,720
kay Lady Jinzhao.

274
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:22,879
Ano?

275
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:25,919
Hindi ba't ganito palagi

276
00:14:25,919 --> 00:14:27,320
nahulog kay Lady Xianlan?

277
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,679
Bakit siya nakikialam dito ngayon?

278
00:14:29,559 --> 00:14:30,440
Nalilito rin ako.

279
00:14:31,039 --> 00:14:32,080
Ang salita ay

280
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:34,519
siya mismo ang humiling nito.

281
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:35,840
Siyempre ginawa niya.

282
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,559
Sasabihin ko rin iyan.

283
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:38,559
Guro,

284
00:14:38,879 --> 00:14:40,240
Gusto niya ng pader sa pagitan ninyo,

285
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,480
mga matataas.

286
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,360
Dapat kang bumuo ng ilan sa iyo.

287
00:14:43,919 --> 00:14:45,840
Nang makapasok si Ginang Yu sa bahay na ito,

288
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,720
isang maling hakbang lang at magugulo na ang lahat.

289
00:14:48,759 --> 00:14:49,799
Gu Jinzhao...

290
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:54,279
Guro,

291
00:14:54,799 --> 00:14:55,840
saan ka pupunta...

292
00:15:09,799 --> 00:15:10,679
Hindi isa pang hakbang.

293
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,559
Kung si Lord Chen ang hinahanap mo,

294
00:15:12,799 --> 00:15:13,960
nasa study siya.

295
00:15:14,519 --> 00:15:15,679
Ito ang tirahan ng mga babae.

296
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:16,960
Hindi ito magiging

297
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,159
maging maayos.

298
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,279
Gusto kong kumonsulta kay Tiya

299
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:25,919
sa ilang mga bagay.

300
00:15:26,279 --> 00:15:27,639
Sa iyong kahusayan sa pag-aaral,

301
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:28,559
ano ang kaya mong gawin

302
00:15:28,559 --> 00:15:29,559
posibleng kailangan ko siyang kumonsulta tungkol dito?

303
00:15:30,399 --> 00:15:31,360
Inilibing niya ang sarili

304
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:32,559
sa iyong pagpapakasal

305
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,279
bawat araw.

306
00:15:34,759 --> 00:15:35,799
Hindi siya tumatanggap ng mga bisita.

307
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,279
Kailangan ko nang hilingin na umalis ka.

308
00:15:38,559 --> 00:15:38,960
Napakabuti.

309
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:41,679
Mabuti naman...

310
00:17:34,519 --> 00:17:35,319
Lima...

311
00:17:36,039 --> 00:17:36,799
Anim...

312
00:17:47,960 --> 00:17:49,240
Bakit si Prinsipe Ningan

313
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,519
umaasa pa rin sa pera natin?

314
00:17:51,839 --> 00:17:53,119
Tatlong beses na kaming nagpadala ng mensahe.

315
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:54,400
Ang totoo,

316
00:17:54,960 --> 00:17:56,039
wala nang natira.

317
00:17:56,519 --> 00:17:57,799
Ang buong sambahayan

318
00:17:58,000 --> 00:17:59,839
ay nasa lalamunan ng isa't isa

319
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,480
sa anumang natitirang mga piraso.

320
00:18:01,759 --> 00:18:03,519
At ginugugol ng prinsipe

321
00:18:03,519 --> 00:18:04,640
mas mabilis kaysa sa kinikita niya.

322
00:18:05,519 --> 00:18:06,680
Sa aking mapagpakumbabang palagay,

323
00:18:06,799 --> 00:18:08,400
hindi sila magiging

324
00:18:08,599 --> 00:18:09,960
pagbabayad sa amin anumang oras sa lalong madaling panahon.

325
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:11,160
Sabi nga...

326
00:18:11,519 --> 00:18:12,799
bahay pa rin ito ng prinsipe.

327
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:14,000
Hindi mawawala ang ganyang pangalan

328
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:15,319
lahat ng halaga nito nang sabay-sabay.

329
00:18:15,559 --> 00:18:16,640
Ano ang iminumungkahi mo?

330
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,359
Ginang Chen

331
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:20,359
ay bastos

332
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:22,000
sa iyo.

333
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,559
Ako ay naging

334
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,759
nag-iisip ng paraan

335
00:18:25,759 --> 00:18:27,000
para masaktan ang likod niya.

336
00:18:27,359 --> 00:18:28,720
Paano mo gagawin iyon?

337
00:18:29,799 --> 00:18:30,799
Bumalik na ang panginoon.

338
00:18:37,759 --> 00:18:38,720
Ano ba kayong dalawa?

339
00:18:39,039 --> 00:18:39,880
nagpaplano dito?

340
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:40,680
Panginoon ko.

341
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:44,079
Nagbabalak laban kay Lord Chen.

342
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:46,160
Ngayon, may kakaiba na

343
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:47,480
sulit i-plot!

344
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:48,200
Sa lahat ng paraan, ituloy mo lang.

345
00:18:53,079 --> 00:18:53,799
Sige.

346
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:02,319
Araw ng pagbubukas.

347
00:19:02,799 --> 00:19:04,200
Bakit mo ako susunduin?

348
00:19:04,440 --> 00:19:05,720
Pwede ka namang maghintay na lang doon.

349
00:19:06,519 --> 00:19:07,000
Ah,

350
00:19:07,319 --> 00:19:08,039
Kasal ni Lian

351
00:19:08,279 --> 00:19:10,359
papalapit na si Yao Wenxiu.

352
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:12,799
Darating ka ba sa gabi bago ang araw,

353
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:15,720
o sa mismong umaga?

354
00:19:16,319 --> 00:19:17,440
Ang umaga.

355
00:19:17,759 --> 00:19:18,640
Ang aking presensya

356
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,200
ay hindi magdudulot sa kanila ng anumang kagalakan.

357
00:19:23,039 --> 00:19:23,759
Jinzhao,

358
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:27,559
Kailangan kong humingi ng pabor sa iyo.

359
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:29,200
Sige.

360
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:32,799
Nais ng mga Mus na…

361
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:34,839
magpadala ng pormal na panukala.

362
00:19:35,039 --> 00:19:35,680
Patawad?

363
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,599
Magsalita ka.

364
00:19:39,599 --> 00:19:41,440
Gusto nilang ipadala ang mga regalo sa kasal!

365
00:19:42,839 --> 00:19:44,720
Hindi lang... sa Daxin.

366
00:19:45,039 --> 00:19:46,640
Maaari ba silang pumunta sa

367
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:47,640
ang ari-arian ni Chen sa halip?

368
00:19:49,039 --> 00:19:49,839
Aba, aba,

369
00:19:50,599 --> 00:19:51,079
kaya hindi siya

370
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:53,039
napakatanga gaya ng dati?

371
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,640
Nagpapabuti siya

372
00:19:56,960 --> 00:19:57,680
sa ibabaw

373
00:19:57,960 --> 00:19:59,119
kakilala.

374
00:20:00,440 --> 00:20:01,839
Ganun ba siya ngayon?

375
00:20:04,279 --> 00:20:05,200
Si Wanxue ba

376
00:20:05,319 --> 00:20:07,200
malapit na ring pagpalain?

377
00:20:09,279 --> 00:20:09,839
Siya nga.

378
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:13,200
Magtatakda tayo ng petsa

379
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:15,440
kasama ang pamilyang Yu sa lalong madaling panahon,

380
00:20:17,839 --> 00:20:18,640
malamang

381
00:20:19,079 --> 00:20:20,240
ngayong taon pa rin.

382
00:20:29,799 --> 00:20:31,160
Mga binibini ko,

383
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:32,640
Ang mga tauhan ni Prinsipe Ningan

384
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:33,720
kinubkob

385
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,240
ang buong lugar!

386
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:36,799
Pinipigilan sila ni Mr. Luo sa labas!

387
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:38,359
Hindi ko pa kailanman

388
00:20:39,559 --> 00:20:40,799
nagkrus ang landas namin.

389
00:20:43,279 --> 00:20:43,759
Sumama

390
00:20:44,079 --> 00:20:44,839
Ginoong Ping,

391
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:46,000
alamin kung ano ito.

392
00:20:46,759 --> 00:20:47,599
Mananatili akong malapit

393
00:20:47,799 --> 00:20:48,680
at manood.

394
00:20:48,759 --> 00:20:49,240
Tama.

395
00:20:53,839 --> 00:20:55,680
Malinis ang rekord namin, ginoo.

396
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,519
Mga buwis na binabayaran sa tamang oras,

397
00:20:56,640 --> 00:20:58,279
makipagkalakalan nang tapat at matuwid.

398
00:20:58,519 --> 00:21:00,240
Dapat may hindi pagkakaunawaan.

399
00:21:02,319 --> 00:21:03,039
Binibini ko!

400
00:21:03,200 --> 00:21:03,839
Ginoong Ping.

401
00:21:05,160 --> 00:21:05,920
Ito si Ginoong Lai,

402
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:07,480
katiwala sa Kanyang Kamahalan

403
00:21:07,839 --> 00:21:08,440
Prinsipe Ningan.

404
00:21:08,559 --> 00:21:09,039
Payagan mo ako

405
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:10,000
para iharap si Ginang Gu Lan,

406
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:11,079
sino ang nagmamay-ari

407
00:21:11,319 --> 00:21:12,240
ang restawran na ito.

408
00:21:13,519 --> 00:21:14,519
Pagbati, aking panginoon.

409
00:21:15,279 --> 00:21:16,440
Si Ginang Gu Lan?

410
00:21:17,359 --> 00:21:18,480
Nakaka-curious naman.

411
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:20,000
Sinabihan kami ng may-ari ng bahay

412
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:21,920
ay si Ginang Chen,

413
00:21:22,079 --> 00:21:23,400
asawa ni Panginoong Chen Yanyun.

414
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:26,359
Kaya ikaw ay... ano, eksakto?

415
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:28,680
Kapatid ko si Ginang Chen.

416
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,359
Ako ang namamahala sa establisyimento na ito

417
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:31,599
sa kanyang ngalan,

418
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:32,759
aking panginoon.

419
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:34,359
Sige, kung ganoon.

420
00:21:35,039 --> 00:21:35,680
Isang simpleng bagay.

421
00:21:36,119 --> 00:21:36,960
Mayroon kaming isang tagapagtanghal

422
00:21:36,960 --> 00:21:38,319
sa aming trabaho,

423
00:21:38,519 --> 00:21:39,559
Xia Xiaohan.

424
00:21:39,920 --> 00:21:41,319
Isang talentong nailahad sa entablado,

425
00:21:42,079 --> 00:21:42,759
matalas ang isip

426
00:21:43,039 --> 00:21:43,880
at kaaya-aya sa paningin,

427
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,880
kinalulugdan ng Kanyang Kamahalan.

428
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:47,359
Hindi pa nagtatagal,

429
00:21:47,359 --> 00:21:48,279
nawala siya

430
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:50,839
nang walang pasabi kahit kanino.

431
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:52,759
May mga tanong akong ginawa,

432
00:21:53,400 --> 00:21:55,480
at bawat daanan

433
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:56,279
humahantong sa

434
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:59,119
ang iyong pinto.

435
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:01,559
Ibigay mo siya sa akin,

436
00:22:01,559 --> 00:22:03,079
aking ginang.

437
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:05,680
Nauubos na ang pasensya ko.

438
00:22:07,559 --> 00:22:08,759
Hindi ba lalaki si Xia Xiaohan?

439
00:22:09,079 --> 00:22:09,720
May itinatago ba silang lalaki sa loob?

440
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:10,279
Ano ang nangyayari?

441
00:22:11,559 --> 00:22:12,359
Panginoon ko.

442
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:15,200
Mga babae lang ang aming pinaglilingkuran.

443
00:22:15,759 --> 00:22:17,119
Bawat lingkod,

444
00:22:17,119 --> 00:22:18,359
bawat kaluluwa sa kawani,

445
00:22:18,559 --> 00:22:19,519
isang babae.

446
00:22:20,079 --> 00:22:21,920
Ang lalaking hinahanap mo

447
00:22:22,359 --> 00:22:24,000
hindi maaaring itago rito.

448
00:22:24,440 --> 00:22:25,839
Natatakot akong naligaw ka.

449
00:22:26,079 --> 00:22:26,599
Ang aking ginang,

450
00:22:27,279 --> 00:22:28,359
handa ka ba talaga

451
00:22:28,519 --> 00:22:30,319
para lumaban sa Kanyang Kamahalan?

452
00:22:30,759 --> 00:22:31,240
Hindi ako maglalakas-loob.

453
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:32,279
Nakaka-curious lang talaga ako,

454
00:22:32,440 --> 00:22:34,279
Ngayon sa lahat ng araw, ang aming unang araw ng pagbubukas,

455
00:22:34,559 --> 00:22:35,880
at dumating ka kasama ang mga lalaki

456
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:37,079
upang palibutan ang lugar.

457
00:22:37,359 --> 00:22:38,960
Iyan ay isang kahanga-hangang pagkakataon.

458
00:22:39,160 --> 00:22:40,200
Wala akong kaalaman

459
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:41,720
ng iyong pambungad.

460
00:22:42,279 --> 00:22:44,359
Ang utos lamang ng Kanyang Kamahalan ang aking sinusunod.

461
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:46,319
Ibigay mo sa akin ang lalaki,

462
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:47,599
o

463
00:22:48,039 --> 00:22:49,279
Hindi na ito magiging usapan.

464
00:22:49,440 --> 00:22:50,000
Mga lalaki,

465
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:50,920
maghanap sa lugar.

466
00:22:51,519 --> 00:22:52,039
Hawakan,

467
00:22:54,279 --> 00:22:54,880
aking panginoon.

468
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:57,839
Isasantabi ang kasal ng kapatid ko

469
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,240
kay Ginoong Chen.

470
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:01,640
Sinalakay ng mga tauhan mo ang aking lugar

471
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,039
sa araw ng aming pagbubukas.

472
00:23:03,319 --> 00:23:04,079
Kung sakaling kumalat ang balita tungkol dito,

473
00:23:04,079 --> 00:23:05,200
masisira ang reputasyon natin.

474
00:23:05,720 --> 00:23:07,440
Hanapin siya, at gagawin ko

475
00:23:07,839 --> 00:23:09,079
sumama sa iyo nang may kagalakan,

476
00:23:09,079 --> 00:23:10,119
nang walang kahit isang salita ng pagtutol.

477
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:12,279
Pero kung wala siya rito,

478
00:23:13,039 --> 00:23:13,880
Kanyang Kamahalan

479
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:15,480
may utang sa atin

480
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:16,480
isang buong pagtutuos.

481
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:18,319
Bawat pagkatalo

482
00:23:18,319 --> 00:23:19,759
nagdurusa tayo ngayon

483
00:23:20,079 --> 00:23:21,720
ay ilalagak sa kaniyang paanan.

484
00:23:22,039 --> 00:23:24,240
Ang mabubuting taong ito ang aking mga saksi.

485
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:25,960
Mayroon ba tayong kasunduan,

486
00:23:26,519 --> 00:23:27,400
aking panginoon?

487
00:23:28,759 --> 00:23:29,599
May utos tayo mula sa itaas!

488
00:23:29,759 --> 00:23:30,440
Tumabi ka!

489
00:23:30,640 --> 00:23:31,119
Linisin ang kalye.

490
00:23:31,559 --> 00:23:32,559
Opisyal na gawain.

491
00:23:32,559 --> 00:23:33,960
Tumabi ka o aarestuhin ka!

492
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:39,960
May mga utos tayo para maghanap

493
00:23:40,599 --> 00:23:42,440
ang mga lugar na ito para sa isang takas!

494
00:23:43,079 --> 00:23:43,519
Gumalaw!

495
00:23:59,200 --> 00:23:59,839
Jinzhao,

496
00:24:00,279 --> 00:24:01,920
Nasa atin na ang mga tauhan ng mahistrado.

497
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:03,240
Magpapadala ba tayo ng mensahe kay Lord Chen?

498
00:24:11,119 --> 00:24:11,759
Ang aking ginang.

499
00:24:13,039 --> 00:24:13,640
Ginoong Ping.

500
00:24:14,559 --> 00:24:15,759
Huwag magtipid ng barya,

501
00:24:16,039 --> 00:24:17,079
kunin ang pinuno

502
00:24:17,079 --> 00:24:18,240
papasok sa isang suite.

503
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:19,480
Makikipag-usap sana ako sa kanya.

504
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:20,559
Ang aking ginang.

505
00:24:29,880 --> 00:24:31,240
Ginoo,

506
00:24:31,519 --> 00:24:32,200
dito mismo.

507
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:50,599
Iwan mo kami.

508
00:24:50,799 --> 00:24:51,240
Sabay-sabay.

509
00:24:54,680 --> 00:24:55,880
Ang aking ginang ay nagpapakita ng ganitong kagandahang-loob,

510
00:24:56,839 --> 00:24:58,200
tama lang

511
00:24:58,200 --> 00:24:59,480
na ibabalik ko ito.

512
00:24:59,880 --> 00:25:01,119
Ang aking kaalaman sa bagay na ito

513
00:25:01,119 --> 00:25:02,440
ay mababaw sa pinakamahusay na paraan.

514
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:03,599
Ngunit

515
00:25:03,759 --> 00:25:05,039
isang ideya ang nananatili:

516
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:07,079
Mayroon ba ang iyong kabit

517
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:07,880
kamakailan lang ay nagkaroon ng kaaway,

518
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:08,920
isa na may kapangyarihan

519
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,839
sapat na para gumalaw laban sa

520
00:25:11,119 --> 00:25:12,559
isang babaeng may ganitong katayuan?

521
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,000
Hindi karaniwan ang mga ganitong kaaway.

522
00:25:16,119 --> 00:25:16,640
